sentences: Mifune began creating his first tracks under the pseudonym Morning Crash, when he began learning how to make computer-aided music.
Mifune has been an opening act for Stromae (Rencontres Trans Musicales of 2013), Madeon (Le Trianon) and Fauve (eighteen representations ).
He composed Saisons (2014), Les cheveux longs (2015) and Atlas (2016), along with a collaboration EP, Croquis n°1 (2015).
